    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《无钥匙：觉醒》是一段穿越梦幻、超现实世界的旅程，现实与幻想之间的界限变得模糊。在这个第一-人称 3D 体验中，您扮演的主角被困在一个神秘、无尽的地方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195200/extras/da584cf5e74f65899371a277ecfe023e.poster.avif?t=1764084410\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195200/extras/da584cf5e74f65899371a277ecfe023e.webm?t=1764084410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195200/extras/da584cf5e74f65899371a277ecfe023e.mp4?t=1764084410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索无尽的走廊和红玫瑰田野，面对简单的隐喻挑战，并遇到奇异的事情生物。那些在你之前发现自己身处这个陌生地方的人已留下留言供你阅读他们最后的想法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195200/extras/0b9320a4615cce1645cb031784221390.avif?t=1764084410\" width=1560 height=906 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏有多种解释，游戏玩法包括步行和跑步，简单的挑战与奇异、隐喻和超现实的场景交替出现，每个岔路口会稍微修改环境和路径。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195200/extras/992f6f359ca699d45c35014aa8176105.poster.avif?t=1764084410\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195200/extras/992f6f359ca699d45c35014aa8176105.webm?t=1764084410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195200/extras/992f6f359ca699d45c35014aa8176105.mp4?t=1764084410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它是关于经历隐喻的情况，在选择路径时观察环境的变化，并通过梦、生和死的镜头来解释你所看到的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195200/extras/0e0aa1425d8461d341f804e689169924.poster.avif?t=1764084410\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195200/extras/0e0aa1425d8461d341f804e689169924.webm?t=1764084410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195200/extras/0e0aa1425d8461d341f804e689169924.mp4?t=1764084410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由一个人使用虚幻引擎开发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
